dirvish-stats is a program which helps determining
        used diskspace from hardlinked dirvish backups


REQUIRED SOFTWARE
-----------------

pypy >= 1.6 or python >= 2.5 recommend
python-gdbm
python-pytc

# if you need the embedded tokyocabinet library (lib/tc)
libtokyocabinet-dev


SUPPORTED PLATTFORMS
--------------------

tested on: python2.4, python2.5, python2.6, pypy1.5, pypy1.6

systems tested:
    - Debian Linux from lenny to unstable
    - BSD (freebsd, mirbsd)
